data.description: Welcome to this exquisite condo in the heart of North Oklahoma City. This well-appointed property boasts two spacious primary suites, each with private bathrooms and walk-in closets. The downstairs features a fully remodeled powder room, gas fireplace, built-in cabinetry and separate dining room. As you step inside, you’ll be greeted by updated wood floors in all general circulation spaces, creating an inviting and elegant ambiance. The restrooms and entryway showcase beautiful ceramic tile, while carpeted stairs provide a cozy transition between levels.The condo has been thoughtfully upgraded with modern plumbing fixtures and brand-new light fixtures. With stainless steel appliances and granite countertops and under-cabinet lighting, make this space a chef's dream. A newly remodeled separate wet/coffee bar adds functionality and style. The design choices feature a harmonious blend of modern elements with color, finishes and fixtures. Combining that with traditional architectural design that includes hardwood detailing throughout, it creates a transitional space that exudes timelessness.Step outside to the hidden back patio, a perfect spot to relax and unwind. The property is surrounded by mature landscaping and offers a quiet environment; also incredibly pet-friendly. The gated community includes a lit tennis court and a newly refreshed swimming pool, providing ample opportunities for leisure and recreation. Located between two private schools and near an elementary school. Situated near the Chisholm Creek area’s up-and-coming developments, you'll have easy access to The Village, Chisholm Creek, Lake Hefner, The Britton District and the diverse array of restaurants and shopping options along Memorial Road. Commuting is a breeze with the Kilpatrick Turnpike, I-235, and I- 74 just minutes away. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of timeless luxury in North Oklahoma City. Contact us to schedule a viewing and make this exceptional condo your new home.
